snippet.title: Amber Heard Responds To Affair Rumors With Leo DiCaprio!
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp Shows Gratitude Towards All His Fans For Supporting Him Against Amber Heard After Huge Win In Court!

✅ Subscribe & HIT that notification bell for more Celebrity Content!

Amber Heard has given a lot to talk about lately, and her supposedly extramarital love affairs have been no exception. Since she and actor Johnny Depp have been in conflict since their separation in 2016, after only 15 months of a tortuous marriage that seemed perfect, the actress has been with different romantic partners. Among her partners during their marriage and after it, is the actor Leonardo DiCaprio, who was supposedly romantically involved with the actress, but what was it that the actor said about the Amber Heard? Does Leo deny all accusations or admit to the secret love affair with the Aquaman actress?
